Am I really someone
who will be praised...

798
01:01:28,190 --> 01:01:29,920
once I disappear from this world?

799
01:01:34,530 --> 01:01:37,599
It's just that what he said kept
popping into my head.

800
01:01:41,039 --> 01:01:43,039
You should get some rest.

801
01:01:44,010 --> 01:01:46,070
Stop agonizing over something
meaningless.

802
01:01:46,269 --> 01:01:48,210
Just think about recovering
and coming back to work.

803
01:02:05,789 --> 01:02:06,789
Hey.

804
01:02:07,230 --> 01:02:08,230
Hey!

805
01:02:11,199 --> 01:02:12,230
What?

806
01:02:13,630 --> 01:02:15,139
Det. Dong Baek?

807
01:02:26,710 --> 01:02:28,349
(If you want to know the truth,
come to the place it all started.)

808
01:04:26,800 --> 01:04:28,139
Seo Yi Soo.

809
01:04:34,179 --> 01:04:37,679
From now on,
I will tell you the real truth.

810
01:04:39,349 --> 01:04:40,349
My brother...

811
01:04:41,349 --> 01:04:42,519
Dong Baek.

812
01:05:27,559 --> 01:05:29,159
Those are records about
someone with supernatural powers.

813
01:05:29,159 --> 01:05:31,369
Someone besides Det. Dong Baek.

814
01:05:31,369 --> 01:05:33,630
Track down Det. Dong's location.
Now.

815
01:05:33,730 --> 01:05:36,599
Tell me everything you people know.

816
01:05:37,440 --> 01:05:38,940
How can I believe you?

817
01:05:39,539 --> 01:05:40,780
I think...

818
01:05:41,809 --> 01:05:43,179
that's when I realized it.

819
01:05:43,179 --> 01:05:44,650
Is that why you killed people...

820
01:05:45,380 --> 01:05:46,750
and began your revenge?

821
01:05:47,420 --> 01:05:50,119
If you think I'm a monster,
kill me. Kill me!

822
01:05:50,119 --> 01:05:51,590
Show me your hands. It's over.

823
01:05:51,590 --> 01:05:53,989
Just keep quiet and watch.
It's going to get serious now.
